videos.headline: Stephens interception stops Miami (OH)
videos.description: Clint Stephens' end zone interception stalls the Red Hawks drive in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Red Hawks take the lead
videos.description: Gus Ragland connects with James Gardner for a 32-yard touchdown pitch and catch in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Ragland extends the lead for the Red Hawks
videos.description: Gus Ragland's 11-yard touchdown run pushes the lead for Miami (OH).

videos.headline: Bowling Green rumbles back
videos.description: Josh Cleveland's 33-yard touchdown run pulls Bowling Green within three in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Harding's interception stops Bowling Green
videos.description: Heath Harding's first interception of the season for Miami (OH) stops the Bowling Green drive.

videos.headline: Morgan finds Wilcox for TD
videos.description: James Morgan and Matthew Wilcox hook up on a 2-yard touchdown pitch and catch to give Bowling Green the lead.

videos.headline: Morgan to Redding strike for big play TD
videos.description: First play of the second half gives us a James Morgan to Teo Redding 75-yard touchdown pass play for Bowling Green.

videos.headline: Ragland to Murphy gets the lead back for the Red Hawks
videos.description: Gus Ragland connects with Jared Murphy for a 36-yard touchdown pass play in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Redding's second TD catch reclaims the lead for  Bowling Green
videos.description: James Morgan and Teo Redding strike again for a 28-yard touchdown pass play to give the Falcons the lead again in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Mayock toe dances down the sideline for a great play
videos.description: Billy Bahl and Luke Mayock connect on a critical 27-yard pass play as Mayock tight ropes the sideline.
